	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ءَاتَيۡنَٰهُمُ ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ يَعۡرِفُونَهُۥ كَمَا يَعۡرِفُونَ </div><div>أَبۡنَآءَهُمۡۖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَإِنَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَرِيقٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ لَيَكۡتُمُونَ ٱلۡحَقَّ وَهُمۡ يَعۡلَمُونَ ٦٤١ </div><div>ٱلۡحَقُّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِن</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> رَّبِّكَ فَلَا تَكُونَنَّ مِنَ <a data-content='الشّاكّين في كتمانهم الحقّ مع العلم به' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡمُمۡتَرِينَ</a> ٧٤١ وَلِكُلّٖ </div><div>وِجۡهَةٌ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>هُوَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مُوَلِّيهَاۖ فَٱسۡتَبِقُواْ ٱلۡخَيۡرَٰتِۚ أَيۡنَ مَا تَكُونُواْ يَأۡتِ بِكُمُ </div><div>ٱللَّهُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>جَمِيعًاۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ قَدِيرٞ ٨٤١ وَمِنۡ حَيۡثُ </div><div>خَرَجۡتَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَوَلِّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَجۡهَكَ شَطۡرَ ٱلۡمَسۡجِدِ ٱلۡحَرَامِۖ وَإِنَّهُۥ لَلۡحَقُّ مِن </div><div>رَّبِّكَۗ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَمَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱللَّهُ بِغَٰفِلٍ عَمَّا تَعۡمَلُونَ ٩٤١ وَمِنۡ حَيۡثُ خَرَجۡتَ </div><div>فَوَلِّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَجۡهَكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> شَطۡرَ ٱلۡمَسۡجِدِ ٱلۡحَرَامِۚ وَحَيۡثُ مَا كُنتُمۡ </div><div>فَوَلُّواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وُجُوهَكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> شَطۡرَهُۥ لِئَلَّا يَكُونَ لِلنَّاسِ عَلَيۡكُمۡ حُجَّةٌ إِلَّا </div><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ظَلَمُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِنۡهُمۡ فَلَا تَخۡشَوۡهُمۡ وَٱخۡشَوۡنِي وَلِأُتِمَّ نِعۡمَتِي </div><div>عَلَيۡكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَعَلَّكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تَهۡتَدُونَ ٠٥١ كَمَآ أَرۡسَلۡنَا فِيكُمۡ رَسُولٗا مِّنكُمۡ </div><div>يَتۡلُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَلَيۡكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ءَايَٰتِنَا <a data-content='يُطهّرهم من الشّرك والمعاصي' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَيُزَكِّيكُمۡ</a> وَيُعَلِّمُكُمُ </div><div><a data-content='القرآن والسّنن والفقه في الدّين' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ وَٱلۡحِكۡمَةَ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَيُعَلِّمُكُم</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مَّا لَمۡ تَكُونُواْ تَعۡلَمُونَ ١٥١ فَٱذۡكُرُونِيٓ </div><div>أَذۡكُرۡكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَٱشۡكُرُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لِي وَلَا تَكۡفُرُونِ ٢٥١ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div>ءَامَنُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direct